TF2 version: http://testserver.resurfed.xyz/maps/surf_hope.bsp....
CS:GO version: https://gamebanana.com/maps/197323

A collaboration map made for Resurfed TF2 contest.
Stage 1 - Blue Raven
Stage 2 - masog
Stage 3 - biji
Bonus - Xtra_festive
Putting the map together - Shadow Sheep

Map is tier 4/5, said to be 5 by most people.
There are triggers that server owners can use for zones.
